OL,3,CIs Ruben Amorim the one to break the
OL,4,Cmould at Manchester United?
OL,6,FRuben Amorim speaks to the media in
OL,7,Fhis first news conference since being
OL,8,Fappointed Manchester United manager,
OL,9,Fas ITV News' Sports Editor Steve Scott
OL,10,Freports
OL,12,FIf success comes with a winning smile
OL,13,Fand charisma, then Ruben Amorim might
OL,14,Fjust be Manchester United's man.
OL,16,FHe is the sixth permanent boss to sit
OL,17,Fin the Old Trafford hot seat since Sir
OL,18,FAlex Ferguson left and none of them
OL,19,Fhas been a resounding or long-lasting
OL,20,Fhit.
