OL,3,CIs Ruben Amorim the one to break the
OL,4,Cmould at Manchester United?
OL,6,FEach had an impressive CV but one by
OL,7,Fone they were sent away with little to
OL,8,Fcelebrate.
OL,10,FIs Amorim the one to break the mould?
OL,11,FCan he turn around a club that used to
OL,12,Fbe feared right across the league and
OL,13,Fis now languishing in mid-table?
OL,15,FHe believes so, but then you'd expect
OL,16,Fhim to say that.
