OL,3,CIs Ruben Amorim the one to break the
OL,4,Cmould at Manchester United?
OL,6,F"I'm a little bit of a dreamer and
OL,7,Fbelieve in myself," he said. "I also
OL,8,Fbelieve in the club. I think we have
OL,9,Fthe same idea, the same mindset so
OL,10,Fthat can help.
OL,12,F"I truly believe in the players also.
OL,13,FI know that you guys (the media) don't
OL,14,Fbelieve a lot in these players, but I,
OL,15,FI believe a lot. I think we, we have
OL,16,Froom to improve and I want to try new
OL,17,Fthings."
