OL,3,CIs Ruben Amorim the one to break the
OL,4,Cmould at Manchester United?
OL,6,FOn Friday at United's Carrington
OL,7,FTraining Ground, the conference room
OL,8,Fwhere Amorim was unveiled was as
OL,9,Fpacked as staffers here can remember.
OL,11,FAfter dithering over Erik ten Hag, who
OL,12,Fgot an unlikely contract extension in
OL,13,Fthe summer, Amorim is the Ineos
OL,14,Fchoice. The first big move from Sir
OL,15,FJim Ratcliffe and his executive team
OL,16,Fsince they took over running football
OL,17,Fmatters at United. They need this to
OL,18,Fwork.
