OL,3,CIs Ruben Amorim the one to break the
OL,4,Cmould at Manchester United?
OL,6,FAmorim has won the League twice with
OL,7,FSporting in Portugal, the first of
OL,8,Fthose ending a 19-year wait for the
OL,9,Fclub.
OL,11,FBut he's never managed a club outside
OL,12,Fhis home country before, and certainly
OL,13,Fnever experienced the scrutiny that is
OL,14,Fnow coming his way, but he does not
OL,15,Fbelieve this is the 'impossible job'.
OL,17,F"Call me naive, but I truly believe
OL,18,Fthat I'm the right guy in the right
OL,19,Fmoment," he said. "I could be wrong,
OL,20,Fbut the earth still will turn, the sun
OL,21,Fwill rise again."
