OL,3,CIs Ruben Amorim the one to break the
OL,4,Cmould at Manchester United?
OL,6,F"I truly believe that I'm the right
OL,7,Fguy for this job," Amorim added.
OL,9,FHowever, he did admit there will be no
OL,10,Fquick fix to turn United's fortunes
OL,11,Faround, saying: "I really don't know
OL,12,Fthe biggest challenge. I will find out
OL,13,Fduring this month.
