OL,3,CIs Ruben Amorim the one to break the
OL,4,Cmould at Manchester United?
OL,6,F"You had here different types of
OL,7,Fcoaches, so the guys that won
OL,8,Feverything like Van Gaal and Mourinho.
OL,9,FYou've had new ones like they knew the
OL,10,Fclub inside out like Solskjaer. Then
OL,11,Fyou have one of the best that there
OL,12,Fwill ever be in the outside, the five
OL,13,Fstrongest leagues - Ten Hag."
