OL,3,CIs Ruben Amorim the one to break the
OL,4,Cmould at Manchester United?
OL,6,F"I don't know, I think we have to
OL,7,Fimprove as a club. We have to
OL,8,Facknowledge that we are in the time
OL,9,Fthat we need time and every coach that
OL,10,Fcomes here needs time," Amorim said.
OL,12,F"But to acknowledge that we also have
OL,13,Fto win games and that's it. We will
OL,14,Ftry to do it our way, in my way and
OL,15,Ftry to win it."
OL,17,FCalm and confident, Amorim's
OL,18,Fperformance was impressive today, but
OL,19,Fhe hasn't taken charge of a single
OL,20,Fgame yet and that of course is when
OL,21,Fthe real business begins.
